\is1 Introduction
\ip This the second letter that we have by Yohan one of the earliest followers of Yeshua. He sent this letter to a chosen woman and her childrenвҖ”presumably meaning вҖҳchosen by GodвҖҷ. Some think this might be referring to a group of believers (in which case, the вҖҳchosen sisterвҖҷ of the closing sentence might also be a congregation). This short letter reminds the recipients that it's necessary to keep following the truth of Yeshua's original teaching and to love each other. It also warns about those who teach that Yeshua was not the messiah (or was not God).
\iot Main components of Yohan's letter
\io1 Greetings \ior 1-3\ior*
\io1 Love and obedience \ior 4-6\ior*
\io1 Guarding the truth \ior 7-11\ior*
\io1 Ending \ior 12-13\ior*
\rem This is still a very early look into the unfinished text of the Open English Translation of the Bible. Please double-check the text in advance before using in public.
\ie
\c 1
\rem /s1 Greetings; Salutation; Truth and love
\p
\v 1 \add This letter is from Yohan\add* the elderВҰ154185 to the chosenВҰ154186 lady and herВҰ154191 childrenВҰ154190 who I genuinely love (as do all the other believers)
\v 2 becauseВҰ154209 of the truthВҰ154211 thatВҰ154212 lives in us andВҰ154217 will be with us forever.
\p
\v 3 We will have graceВҰ154228, mercyВҰ154229, and peaceВҰ154230 in truthВҰ154246 and love from \nd GodВҰ154233\nd* the father and from his son \nd Yeshua\nd* the \nd messiahВҰ154239\nd*.
\s1 Stick to the original message
\rem /s1 Truth and Love; Live in the Truth
\p
\v 4 I was so happy that I foundВҰ154252 some of yourВҰ154257 childrenВҰ154256 living out the truthВҰ154260 as per the commandВҰ154262 that the fatherВҰ154268 gave us.
\v 5 \x + \xo 5: \xt Yhn 13:34; 15:12,17.\x*SoВҰ154269 now I'm requesting you, lady, (not making some new commandВҰ154276, butВҰ154269 one that we've had since the beginningВҰ154287) that we all need to love each other
\v 6 where the definition of love is obeying God's commandsВҰ154300. This is the commandВҰ154308 about walking in love that you all heardВҰ154314 from the beginningВҰ154316
\v 7 because many false preachers have entered the worldВҰ154329 who don'tВҰ154331 believe that \nd Yeshua\nd* is the messiah who cameВҰ154325 as a human. Any person like that is a deceiverВҰ154341 andВҰ154342 against the messiah.
\p
\v 8 So make sure that you all don'tВҰ154349 lose what you've worked for, but rather go on to receive a full rewardВҰ154357.
\p
\v 9 \nd AnyoneВҰ154375\nd* who doesn't stay with the \nd messiah'sВҰ154375\nd* teaching or adds more to it doesn't have \nd GodВҰ154376\nd*вҖ”it's the person who continues in the his teaching thatВҰ154362 has both the fatherВҰ154390 and the son with them.
\v 10 If anyoneВҰ154397 comes to youВҰ154400 all and doesn't bringВҰ154408 this same message, don't accept that person into your houseВҰ154413, and don't tell them that it's good
\v 11 becauseВҰ154421 anyone who encourages those people is participating in the evilВҰ154430 that they're spreading.
\s1 Closing off
\rem /s1 Conclusion; Final Words; Final Greetings
\p
\v 12 I've got many things that I wanted to write to you about, butВҰ154441 paperВҰ154440 and inkВҰ154442 aren'tВҰ154437 working for me so I'll try to come and then we can talk directly because I want you all to experience genuine happiness.
\p
\v 13 YourВҰ154472 sister'sВҰ154471 childrenВҰ154469 (and she's also a chosenВҰ154474 one) send their greetingsВҰ154466 also.
